shares the generator's blind spots,
and it will constantly miss exactly

228
00:14:41,995 --> 00:14:46,005
the errors the generator was prone
to make And yeah, if one judge can't

229
00:14:46,005 --> 00:14:51,415
be trusted, we-- easy to-- instinct
is to use several and vote, right?

230
00:14:52,405 --> 00:14:56,555
This is right in spirit and
usually wrong in execution, and

231
00:14:56,595 --> 00:14:58,465
