232
00:14:59,035 --> 00:15:03,635
So if you take three judges from the
same model family and average them,

233
00:15:03,825 --> 00:15:06,415
you have not built a robust verifier.

234
00:15:06,955 --> 00:15:11,175
You've built three correlated copies
of the same biases and averaged

235
00:15:11,175 --> 00:15:14,905
them which sharpens your confidence
