236
00:15:15,525 --> 00:15:20,035
So they share self pre- preference
they share position bias, they

237
00:15:20,035 --> 00:15:23,655
share the same holes because
they share the same training.

238
00:15:24,145 --> 00:15:26,725
Averaging correlated
errors doesn't cancel them.

239
00:15:26,955 --> 00:15:32,455
It launders them into a number that looks
