257
00:16:48,645 --> 00:16:50,795
instrument and being silently wrong.

258
00:16:51,625 --> 00:16:55,695
And the cleanest practical rule
that falls out of the literature

259
00:16:55,735 --> 00:16:59,285
is almost embarrassingly simple,
