260
00:16:59,895 --> 00:17:03,585
Never let a model be the
sole judge or… of itself.

261
00:17:03,755 --> 00:17:08,155
If your agent runs on GPT, GPT should
not be the only thing grading GPT.

262
00:17:08,655 --> 00:17:12,705
Pair it with judges that doesn't
share training and treat the places

263
00:17:12,705 --> 00:17:16,095
where you disagree as a live map
of where your system risk actually

264
00:17:16,095 --> 00:17:19,515
is, and the disagreement isn't a
