265
00:17:19,915 --> 00:17:24,125
It is your verification So the
unit of replication isn't a judge.

266
00:17:24,175 --> 00:17:28,385
It's a panel of deliberately different
judges plus a model of how each one is

267
00:17:28,385 --> 00:17:32,525
