306
00:20:12,565 --> 00:20:14,535
Someone already wrote down the algorithm.

307
00:20:14,575 --> 00:20:17,555
It just wasn't pointed at the judges yet.

308
00:20:18,055 --> 00:20:21,625
But the reason I care about the
