309
00:20:21,795 --> 00:20:23,655
It's the stance it forces.

310
00:20:24,055 --> 00:20:28,905
A static Ansible encodes an
assumption that you already know

311
00:20:29,085 --> 00:20:32,425
how to verify, and you're frozen
