00:20:54,915 --> 00:21:00,435
So routing is what keeps verification
honest, and the ground moves.

318
00:21:00,695 --> 00:21:03,775
The config-frozen version isn't simpler.

319
00:21:04,265 --> 00:21:09,835
It's just wrong more slowly and silently,
which is the exact failure we started

